{"tid":847410,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呼籲各位以後遇到大陸人問路請用法定語言回答","createTime":"2018-10-04T07:01:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T07:59:22.000Z","uid":198834,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3e8bd0d19e3beaf68024cf2cb01d4d4ef7ece064","tid":847410,"uid":198834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T07:01:59.000Z","msg":"唔係話唔想幫手<br />\n但係問人係咪都應該畀返啲誠意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出嚟旅行仲以為自己喺屋企咁<br />\n好似奉旨人哋要用蝗語答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港嘅法定語文係中文同英文<br />\n<strong>文字</strong>方面係指正題中文同埋英文<br />\n而<strong>語言</strong>方面就係指粵語同埋英語<br />\n<br />\n呼籲各位以後見到大陸人問路<br />\n請用香港人嘅語言回答<br />\n即係廣東話或者英語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢聽得明就聽 唔明就罷就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"797d3bb4b382c1ae0bc2922bb65c6980a80a067a","tid":847410,"uid":25170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T07:04:42.000Z","msg":"次次都用英文答<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽唔明就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59531d5ef34a3b2bae413b2339d103042acd9de","tid":847410,"uid":205928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T07:06:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/150618_f64a40628825c2521792c1cbd6573fd4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F150618_f64a40628825c2521792c1cbd6573fd4.png&h=38d4c9d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f5161951587e9488a4b453b5b6e1623126ff00a","tid":847410,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"797d3bb4b382c1ae0bc2922bb65c6980a80a067a","tid":847410,"uid":25170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T07:04:42.000Z","msg":"次次都用英文答<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 